# MailHarvest v3 — Walkthrough

## What Changed

| Area | Change |
|------|--------|
| **Navigation** | Split into 2 pages: landing → scraper (no more scrolling) |
| **Email Validation** | DNS MX + SMTP RCPT TO + catch-all detection |
| **Suggestions** | Typo fixes, domain corrections, re-scrape hints for invalid emails |
| **Export** | Excel now includes Validation Status + Validation Note columns |
| **Status Filter** | Filter table by Valid / Catch-All / Invalid / Unchecked |

